\par play, as soon, he adds, as he "can find the right ink." Hasn't been
\par able to get hold of any that just suited him.
\par 
\par But much more important to his mind, apparently, than this play is
\par another mission in which he has become involved. He is going to have
\par himself "mapped," that is, have his horoscope cast. Yes, by one of the
\par ladies of his party, who, it appears, is eminent as a professor of this
\par science, now rapidly coming into a period of great vogue. When he has
\par supplied her with the data concerning his birth she will reveal to him
\par the course of his career through 1922.
\par 
\par On a number of the tables are cards marked "Reserved." Around two sides
\par of the room upholstered seats running the length of the wall seat
\par couples in greater intimacy of t\'eate-\'e0-t\'eate side by side before their
