\par harvest wonderful.  Let the ears of a guilty people tingle with truth,
\par and seventy millions sigh for the righteousness which exalteth nations,
\par in this drear day when human brotherhood is mockery and a snare.  Thus
\par in Thy good time may infinite reason turn the tangle straight, and
